{"content": "I need to multiply 470 \u00d7 a98 in base 11.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 470 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 470\u2081\u2081 = 4\u00d711\u00b2 + 7\u00d711\u00b9 + 0\u00d711\u2070\n- = 4\u00d7121 + 7\u00d711 + 0\n- = 484 + 77 + 0\n- = 561\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert a98 (base 11) to base 10**\n- a98\u2081\u2081 = 10\u00d711\u00b2 + 9\u00d711\u00b9 + 8\u00d711\u2070\n- = 10\u00d7121 + 9\u00d711 + 8\n- = 1210 + 99 + 8\n- = 1317\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n- 561 \u00d7 1317 = 738,837\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 738,837 back to base 11**\n- 738,837 \u00f7 11 = 67,167 R 0\n- 67,167 \u00f7 11 = 6,106 R 1\n- 6,106 \u00f7 11 = 555 R 1\n- 555 \u00f7 11 = 50 R 5\n- 50 \u00f7 11 = 4 R 6\n- 4 \u00f7 11 = 0 R 4\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 465110\n\n**465110**", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 363, "completion_tokens": 392}